# ==============================================================================
# NOTES
# ==============================================================================

# 1. REQUIRED APIs (Minimum to start):
#    - FRED_API_KEY (economic data)
#    - At least one stock data source (Polygon, Alpha Vantage, or use Yahoo Finance free)

# 2. Yahoo Finance (yfinance Python library):
#    - FREE, unlimited, no API key required
#    - Works out of the box for stocks, forex, crypto, commodities
#    - 15-minute delayed data

# 3. Database-First Architecture:
#    - All downloaded data goes into PostgreSQL
#    - Never fetches from internet again (until 1-hour refresh)
#    - Users see instant data from database

# 4. 1-Hour Refresh:
#    - Background service runs every hour
#    - Updates database silently
#    - Zero user impact

# 5. Security:
#    - NEVER commit this file to git
#    - Use strong passwords in production
#    - Rotate API keys regularly
#    - Use environment-specific .env files (.env.dev, .env.prod)

